T}
_
T{
Other $\-options
T}	T{
\fB$<option name>\fP
T}	T{
\fB<option name>\fP
T}
_
.TE
.sp
Most applications should use the OP_QUERY syntax, with \(dq$query\(dq, \(dq$orderby\(dq, and so on, and rely on the driver to convert to the new syntax if needed.
